				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I thought of a great idea that I think Verant should give Magicians.
<br />

<br />
We need a spell that will summon a robe that has a "Must Equip Casting Time: 20.0" single charge of snare and legs with a "Must Equip Casting Time: 20.0" single charge of root.  Of course the items should be lore.  This would balance us with wizards in terms of CC Ability.  What do you all think of this? 
<br />

<br />
To make this balanced it should cost about 500-600 mana to summon.<br />_________________<br />Sage Sumonweiner
<br />
65 Magician
<br />
Stromm</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
