				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I find it frustrating that many mages seem to feel we should have access to every spell line in the game.  I don't think snare or root would make us any more desirable in groups, as (in the limited amount of grouping I do) it appears that those other classes are chosen for reasons beyond those two spells.  We're DPS, and LDON has certainly helped others to realize this fact.  Personally, I firmly believe we do get root, it's called an earth pet.  Yo-Yo rooting is one of my preferred soloing styles, I'd just as soon let my pet use the mana than I (yes, I know it's not mana consuming for them, but you see my point).
<br />

