				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">define soloing 'effictively'
<br />
i can't solo as well as a wiz/dru/nec but i can still solo pretty well i think.  in fact i still do to do AAs.  there's lots of places in pop you can solo but there's a trick to it, it's called being smart enough to adapt to new circumstances.  you have to know what you are capable of, know where you're trying to hunt...and then pick the method of killing the mob that is best in that case.
<br />

<br />
hint: this method usually is NOT pet tank and healing, and if you attempt to use that method you will die.
<br />

<br />
grouping is a combo of 3 things:
<br />
your reputation (as long as you're not some total ass)
<br />
your skills (if you suck you won't get asked to come back a second time)
<br />
your personality (make friends, friends become groups later)
<br />

<br />

<br />
that being said...
<br />
i still maintain i can solo as well as i could before pop, just using different methods.
<br />
i regularly get ldon or planes groups, and am routinely bugged to do Tak ldons even while i'm busy with other stuff.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
